# User Story 1: I want to create a new customer record in Odoo so that I can manage their information effectively.

    Equivalence Class: Valid information, Missing Information, Invalid Information
    Boundary Value: minimum and maximum value limit for each field

# User Story 2: I want to search for a specific product in Odoo so that I can add it to a sales order.

    Equivalence Class: Valid Information, Partial Information, Invalid Information
    Boundary Value: Minimum and Maximum limit of characters that can be entered in the search bar
# User Story 3: I want to track inventory levels in Odoo so that I can order products before they run out.

    Equivalence Class: Current Inventory Level, Initial Inventory Level, Reorder Point
    Boundary Value: Minimum and Maximum value of Current Inventory Level and Reorder Point


